data.title: Prime Minister Meets President Abbas
data.meta_description: Prime Minister Paul Martin will meet the President of the Palestinian Authority, Mahmoud Abbas, on Friday, May 27, 2005.
data.text: Prime Minister Paul Martin will meet the President of the Palestinian Authority, Mahmoud Abbas, on Friday, May 27, 2005. 3:00 pm Prime Minister Martin meets President Abbas Room 309S Centre Block, Parliament Hill (Photo opportunity at the beginning of the meeting) 4:30 pm Prime Minister Martin and President Abbas hold a joint media availability Reading Room Centre Block, Parliament Hill (Open coverage) 6:30 pm Prime Minister Martin hosts a dinner for President Abbas 9th Floor, Tower A Lester B. Pearson Building 125 Sussex Drive (Open coverage of remarks at beginning of dinner) -30- For Information: PMO Press Office: (613) 957-5555
